des: "A creamy chocolate shake with a nice light banana flavor that I came up with one night. This recipe is for one party mug-sized shake. I'm not normally a fan of banana-flavored drinks, but this milkshake tastes amazing!"
ins: Combine chocolate ice cream, milk, banana, ice cubes, sugar, and vanilla extract in a Magic Bullet(R) party mug. Blend until smooth, 1 to 2 minutes.
